title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 1PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 1PM” game were:
3-9-9-2
(three, nine, nine, two)
